{"tid":1578639,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【監控城巿】調查：75國發展中國式AI監控系統 華為屬主要技術供應商","createTime":"2019-09-18T08:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T08:17:51.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"618adede8d61a02a8c6345452cf23fb20c906803","tid":1578639,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190918/large/1568771652_c63b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190918%2Flarge%2F1568771652_c63b.jpg&h=8270389b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國街頭有嚴謹的監察系統(美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n美國華府智庫卡內基國際和平基金會（Carnegie Endowment for International Peace）周二發表調查報告指，發現有多達75個國家正發展類似中國的人工智能監察系統，包括民主國家如美國、法國，當中以中國科技巨擎華為作為主要的全球技術供應商，報告又指不少國家以發展「智能城市」為名，在公眾地方安裝感應器、鏡頭等。<br />\n<br />\n團隊收集公開資料和新聞報道的紀錄，發現很多國家政府也發展監察民眾的系統，當中包括人臉辨識的系統，不只是極權國家，實行開放民主制度的國家如美國和法國也榜上有名。報告又指各國的監察系統背後，有不少人工智能監察技術支援是由中國公司華為和海康威視（Hikvision）提供，另外也有日本公司NEC及萬國商業機器（IBM）、Palantir、思科（Cisco）。<br />\n<br />\n負責研究的非牟利組織卡內基國際和平基金會成員兼樹城州立大學（Boise State University）助理教授的費爾德斯坦（Steven Feldstein）指︰「我希望市民問更尖銳的問題，了解這種科技如何使用，以及有甚麼影響。」<br />\n<br />\n報告指很多市政府以「智能城市」系統加裝一系列的感應器、鏡頭和其他可連上網的儀器，以收集資料及傳送訊息。由華為提供的儀器包括有管理交通和節能功能，但也越來越多用於公眾監察和保安上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190918/60056405?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60056405%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87EvjxvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=c9a8c859\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190918%2F60056405%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=7aef33c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190918/60056405?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"a9de4235f020fb1480139118d14d63c6eac09aa8","tid":1578639,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:15:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1a1c6192d5abc4c44118069b925fc047361bf85","tid":1578639,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T08:16:29.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全球響應「929全球集會抗赤納粹」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全世界一齊對準極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1577380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1577380</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hWqVmOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhWqVmOV.jpg&h=075c7745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1tov9s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1tov9s.png&h=0af09f95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3dd8c0d13962a123e309391da5e1bb93258ee6d"